result.execSummary:
The defendant Alan David Wick was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Alan David Wick is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Alan David Wick was found guilty of Unlawful Phone Use-Threatens Harm, a class B misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 947.012(1)(a).
  • Alan David Wick was found guilty of Disorderly Conduct, a class B misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 947.01(1).
